              "lessonLabel": "Lesson 25",
              "title": "30m Spiritual Formation: Grades 10-11 - Lesson 25",
              "body": "⍞ Materials: God of all Things\n\n➜ INTRO\nThis is a book all about things.  But the things can point us to God.  So, really, this is a book all about things and God and how we can be reminded of him when we see and interact with the things of this world.  There are new wonders to see all around us!\n\nMaybe a chart, diagram, or drawing for some of the chapters would be a good way to narrate.  Or, maybe writing a poem or a song about each item might make sense to capture the truths of the chapter.  Try a haiku with 5,7, and 5 syllables for each line. See what works well for you.\n \n➜ READ & NARRATE\nForeword, Introduction, Ch.1-2",
              "teacherNotes": "",
